sellerCard.description: Hi, My name is Rajinder Kaur. I am a web designer and developer. I love working on Fiverr,  I've over 10 years of experience in development. Let's get in touch and start working on your dream projects!

description.content:
Hello!


I'm Rajinder Kaur. I am a wordpress developer with 9+ years of experience. I will design and develop a professional wordpress website. It will be an eye-catching, modern, fully responsive website. I have already designed and developed more than 500+ WordPress websites.


What services do I offer in this gig?


  • Fully Completed Website Development with Figma Design
  • Custom E-commerce Functionality
  • Web On-Page SEO
  • Custom WordPress blog
  • Theme Customization
  • WooCommerce Integration & Setup
  • Backup, Cloning & Migration
  • Performance & SEO Friendly
  • Web Security
  • Landing Page
  • Speed optimized
  • Multilingual store
  • Multi-Currency


Why Choose me?


Deliver unique and quality WordPress websites

More than 9+ years of experience

High-quality work until 100% Satisfaction

Unlimited revisions

Quick turnaround and fast response.


Friendly customer relationships are at the epicenter of our services along with 100% quality work and satisfaction.


Let's get started on your project now! 

Free Consultation Services for startups and new businesses.
